headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: By Alan J John - Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: 2022 has surely been a mixed year for Virat Kohli as he had some incredible highs and lows.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: There were questions on his form and even his place in T20I squad following a string of below-par performances.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: However, the star batter has turned things around during the Asia Cup and has actually turned 2022 into one of his best years in the shortest format of the game.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: At the Asia Cup, Kohli was able to end his international century drought as he brought up his maiden ton against Afghanistan.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: The Indian star was the second-highest run-getter in the tournament and carried the form into Australia for the T20 World Cup.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: Kohli currently has 220 runs in the tournament, which makes him the highest run-getter at this point with a staggering average of 220.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: The Indian star is fourth on the highest run-getters in T20Is this year with 705 runs to his name at an average of 58.75.

headlines: Virat Kohli's dream T20I run in 2022
description: Given how his place in the side was questioned at the beginning of the year, Kohli has shown that he is one of the best in T20Is.
